712610f-a.title: Manhattan: 40th Street (East) - 2nd Avenue
712610f-a.text:
East 40th Street, north side, east of Second Avenue.
Outstanding is one of the Tudor City units at First
Avenue. View 2 is photographed northward from the
new roadway that leads to the Queens-Midtown Tunnel.
